						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone set up on the tank bund.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription engraved in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">13th century A.D.,</hi> records the death of <hi rend="bold">Holeya-Nāyaka,</hi> who fought with <hi rend="bold">Baicheya</hi> and died in the presence of a <hi rend="italic">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvar</hi> (name doubtful). The title <hi rend="italic">Ujeniya-Puravarādhīs11vara</hi> indicates that the chief belonged to the family of the <hi rend="bold">Guttas.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
